p.d: Although ‘Angels of Glory’ Martial Arts Masters’ Gala is the first event organized by the Iron Angels Foundation, created earlier in 2016, its scale and sport ambitions are impressive. The fight card contains top names in kickboxing, MMA, muay thai and brazilian jiu-jitsu: Dawid Kasperski, Iwona Nieroda, Wojciech Kosowski, Michał Królik, and Arkadiusz Kaszuba.
